- unified marshalling of GIArgument and GValues
- use it for properties access and signal marshalling.
- signals using native lgi GClosure implementation instead of detour
  through libffi.
- GValue - support for STRV and GValueArray.
- Gio: async->coro wrappers.
- Gio: modifiable buffer as input for _read methods.
- Gtk: Container.child handling
